              "body": "There is a double usage of the word \"use\". I recommend to write instead: \r\n\r\nThe exact conditions under which S-HBS certificates may be used is left to certificate policies. However, the recommended scenarios for deploying S-HBS as described in [SP800208] can be used as a guideline:",
