          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 81,
              "body": "I don't know.  We're not being prescriptive/restrictive here, we're just giving some examples of use cases, people can still use these as they want.  But the group wanted specific use cases, and I don't think adding in a more general case like this would be wise.",
